lunar = Lunar(1990, 1, 29)
expect_lunar = Converter.Solar2Lunar(Converter.Lunar2Solar(lunar))
assert lunar == expect_lunar
lunar = Lunar(2018, 2, 30)
expect_lunar = Converter.Solar2Lunar(Converter.Lunar2Solar(lunar))
assert lunar == expect_lunar
lunar = Lunar(2012, 4, 4)
expect_lunar = Converter.Solar2Lunar(Converter.Lunar2Solar(lunar))
assert lunar == expect_lunar
lunar = Lunar(2012, 4, 4, True)
expect_lunar = Converter.Solar2Lunar(Converter.Lunar2Solar(lunar))
assert lunar == expect_lunar
